                            <comment id="15143768" author="lin@exabeam.com" created="Fri, 12 Feb 2016 00:20:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=zsxwing&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;zsxwing&quot;&gt;zsxwing&lt;/a&gt; I created the PR, please review at your convenience. We are running a patched server but if this can get into 2.0.0 it would be very helpful for us.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
